title: Cyann's Cycle (1995) cbr
description:
As a pandemic fever threatens to kill a good proportion of the males on the planet olh, Cyann, daughter of the rich aristocrat Lazuli Olsimar, leads an expedition to the planet ilo intent on discovering a cure for the disease.

As the search for a cure is brought to an end on ilo, her adventures continue on other planets, beginning with Aldaal, and going on then to Marcade.

enjoy
